<item>
            <title>[LU-4784] refresh of samba share</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4784</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Our filesystem is exported via samba. When a user modify directory content on a lustre client these changes don&apos;t apper on share until the f5 key is pressed on windows client. Otherwise, when same operation is executed directly on the node that export filesystem (a xen virtual machine) the share reflect the changes immediately. How we can fix this problem ? &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>rhel5.7.samba3x-3.5.4-0.83, windows 7</environment>
        <key id="23782">LU-4784</key>
            <summary>refresh of samba share</summary>
